NAME
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::CheckChangeLog - Dist::Zilla with Changes check

VERSION
    version 0.01

SYNOPSIS
        # dist.ini
        [CheckChangeLog]

        # or
        [CheckChangeLog]
        filename = Changes.pod

DESCRIPTION
    The code is mostly a copy-paste of ShipIt::Step::CheckChangeLog

